Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inferior Terran scum! Don't think\Nthat you'll get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Kataphrakt that defeated Sir Vlad\Nwas orange in color, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every last Terran\Nis the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Sky Carrier carried the Argyre.\NYou saw it happen, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... He was killed by\Nthat devious orange bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only two Orbital Knights\Nhave been defeated{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}by Terran units,\NSir Vlad and Sir Trillram.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...when Sir Trillram was defeated, Princess\NAsseylum was with that orange Kataphrakt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to this Sky Carrier's data,\Nthe ship that it was aboard{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was on a\Nsouth-southwesterly course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no hard evidence.\NIt may merely be a coincidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:01:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But right now, this is the only lead\Nthat I have to go on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That battle on Tanegashima...\NMy big brother fought in it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was killed in action.\NMurdered, rather. By you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magbaredge is the name of\Nthe family that adopted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My birth name was Humeray.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your best friend was my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit overhead\Nis in a nosedive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three others closing in\Nfrom our flanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's on a collision course\Nwith the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit! Last!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We won't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Out of ammo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him... How long is he going to\Ncontinue making me look the fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out in the Tharsis.\NPrepare me a Sky Carrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Abide a moment, Count Cruhteo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Saazbaum,\Nwhy do you stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not request that\NI capture him alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do not wish him to notice your\Npursuit and alter his destination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish to know where\Nhe intends to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that he made\Nuse of the Audience Chamber?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he is a spy,\Nsurely he has accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall track him\Nfrom above.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it stopped\Nthe enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's infighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who knows?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They might just be fighting over\Nwho gets to make the kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either is fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:05:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the enemy of my enemy isn't\Nmy friend, he might still be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What clan does this\N interloper belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This area has already been\Nlaid claim to by Femieanne!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will not tolerate you\Ntaking liberties here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my messengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Botis' fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lt. Marito!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lt. Marito! Are you all right?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humeray!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grab on, Humeray!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Marito...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humeray!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll get you\Nout of there, Humeray!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't land a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've put distance between us.\NWhich means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Control! Open the well dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mustang 22!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizuka's brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cover your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cover your ears, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A hidden dock?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Engine status?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hull status?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holding together, barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, taking on water!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make a break\Nfor the dock up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-All ahead full!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Inaho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mustang 11!\NWe're going, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nao, what do you think you're doing?\NDon't run off like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could say the same to you, Yuki.\NWho's defending the ship?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen here, you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machine gun fire.\NTarget: the rock above the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What does that orange\NKataphrakt have up its sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now let's deal with\Nthat Ashura over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Landing Castle will soon reach airspace\Nwhere we can scan the Japanese archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we enter the detection area, scan\Nfor the Sky Carrier stolen by Slaine Troyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Princess Asseylum is alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have seen her\Nwith my own two eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milord Saazbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have located the\Nspecified craft.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is above Tanegashima in the\Nsouthwestern Japanese archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be engaging\NFemieanne's Kataphrakt, Hellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tanegashima, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard anything about there\Nbeing a base like this on Tanegashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever it is, let's get\Neveryone off the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?! Lt. Marito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to breathe in\Nthe smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuating the noncombatants\Nhas top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then the wounded!\NLeave no one behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuribi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mustang Platoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inko and the others\Naren't on the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're still fighting out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're using themselves as decoys\Nto give us time to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit!\NNext, right 3 mil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To attack the assault ship, it has\Nto break through all that rock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To increase their impact,\Nthey have to increase their speed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To accelerate using a rocket,\Nyou have to have distance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the distance\Nis far enough,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}throw off the angle just a little,\Nand it'll miss its mark by a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit, 4 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heading this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not a problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Martian attack craft\Nwill cover us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You dare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on\Naround here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuki. Let's attack the\Nenemy Kat directly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you saying?!\NWe're no match for that thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not so sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It might be all bark\Nand no bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inko. I need to borrow\Nyour handgun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blocks 11 and 12,\Nevacuation confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuation of Block 8\Nis also complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.\NWe should get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any word from Mustang Platoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is pray, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Magbaredge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mizusaki? Why aren't you leading\Nthe refugees away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had them take shelter in a cargo\Nroom up ahead for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there's something that\NI want you to see, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did this happen...\Nbecause I came to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't come, there would\Nhave been no assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there had been no assassination,\Nthis war never would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People would not have been\Nmade to suffer unjustly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that. Because to these people,\Nall Martians are the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is that even possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't the slightest, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of installation is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Milady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a Martian Kataphrakt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did it-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't just one meteor\Nthat fell here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One hit the shore and\Nformed the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the other... ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then this machine was-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The demon we\Nsaw 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always figured it had been annihilated\Nin the damage of Heaven's Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a touching reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me\Nthat we seized it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean that\N Lt. Marito's Tanegashima Report
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was buried so they could\Nkeep this a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...could that be all\Nthere is to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Capt. Magbaredge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world... is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Orange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you doing, Nao?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Ashura over there hasn't\Nbudged from that spot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All it does is repeat\Nthe same attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure that they're\Nits only weapons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I need now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cover us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darn it, Nao!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Opening contact channel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be quick.\NWhat are you armed with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have about 20 howitzer rounds.\NAnd you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}HE rounds, 9.\NThen I'm dry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't do it, Nao!\NThat's a Martian-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Yuki.\NWe'll talk later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Hellas' fists increase their hardness\Nby becoming a single, giant molecule.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No bullet can destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, one of the fists\Nwas destroyed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their molecular structure probably\Nreverts when their fingers move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Patch me into the signal\Nfrom your stabilizers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We use a different standard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all right. I'll convert it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here it comes, Bat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marax!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Him and his crazy stunts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that a good idea?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. His crazy stunts\Ntend to be the right move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pull them closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One left!\NGet directly behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their tails have no armor, which means\Ntheir engines are also vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two more coming in\Nfrom aft!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Course one-seven-five.\NFly parallel to the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You only remember you have\Nteammates when you need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold that course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Botis... Marax...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ronove... Halphas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raum... Vine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you harm\Nmy children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll attack it simultaneously.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me no choice, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It flew away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's gained distance!\NIt's accelerating this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use your rifle to throw off\Nits trajectory!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too big for a rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too heavy with you aboard!\NI can't dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crush you\Nlike the bugs you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost on us, Bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet, Orange!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It dodged me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He stalled out\Nto lose altitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't pull out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The same trick won't\Nwork on me twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A flying ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A battleship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Princess Asseylum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Terrans have no Aldnoah!\NHow could they have such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flying enemy craft closing in\Nfrom 12 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Collision course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy Terrans!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brace for impact, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you... I'm still-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Martians... will pay\Nfor Father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum,\NI've found you at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your princess was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in spite of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...why are you\Nlooking for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You knew that the princess\Nwas alive. So why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to Her Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Answer my question first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait... Are you intending to\Nexploit her to your own ends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she's exploited,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do you have a problem\Nwith that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are my enemy.
